#: chaotic_pfc.dynamics.maps.henon_filtered:3 of
msgid ""
"The quadratic nonlinearity acts on a weighted combination of the two most"
" recent state samples, ``z = c_0 · x_1 + c_1 · x_2``, rather than on a "
"single sample. This is the smallest non-trivial case of "
":func:`henon_order_n`."
msgstr ""

