"Optional explicit initial state, shape ``(Nc,)``. If ``None``, a random "
"state is drawn from ``Uniform(0, 0.5)`` per component."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.dynamics.maps.henon_order_n:21 of
msgid ""
"Optional external driving signal, shape ``(steps,)``. When provided, "
"replaces the self-driving term at each iteration."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.dynamics.maps.henon_order_n:23 of
